      <div class="card-desc">Ten blocks. The 15-minute neighbourhood. Students redesign a Chennai area across 8 urban land uses, quantify the trade-offs (access, housing, green-blue, heat, flood, equity, mobility), and present at the school's environmental showcase to a real municipal audience. The Urban Planner + Equity & Resilience AI partners introduced.</div>
